No, Huan'er.

99
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:52,670
Well...

100
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:55,900
It's not that we're forcing you
to go to universities in the province.

101
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:56,510
Yes.

102
00:03:56,670 --> 00:03:57,420
It's mainly because

103
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:59,020
we're a little worried.

104
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,110
Think about it.

105
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:02,350
If you have a headache,

106
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:02,830
right?

107
00:04:02,900 --> 00:04:04,180
I can come over immediately.

108
00:04:04,270 --> 00:04:04,830
Besides,

109
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:05,830
