117
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:13,860
You're outside.

118
00:04:13,990 --> 00:04:15,300
Don't cry.

119
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:16,230
Calm down.

120
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:17,740
If you're really sick,

121
00:04:17,990 --> 00:04:19,820
I can't see you

122
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:23,150
