123
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:23,990
Alright.

124
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:25,500
Don't...

125
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:28,500
Actually, universities outside
the province aren't bad either.

126
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:32,260
It's just that what should I do
if I miss you?

127
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,500
Mom, I'm just going to university.

128
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:36,260
I'll come back often, okay?

129
00:04:36,350 --> 00:04:37,380
Okay?

130
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:38,550
Don't cry.

131
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:40,670
If there's no other way, I...

132
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:42,860
I'll apply to Wuan University, okay?

133
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:46,380
Wuan University?

134
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:48,180
Wuan University is actually quite good.

135
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:48,550
Yes.

136
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:49,470
Really.

137
00:04:49,470 --> 00:04:49,820
Yes.

138
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:51,150
I think Wuan University is good.

139
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,180
What would you like to eat?

140
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,760
I'll make it for you right away.

141
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:57,350
Let's go.

142
00:04:58,030 --> 00:04:58,710
Hurry.

143
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:09,860
How comfortable.

144
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:14,220
How did you all
fill out your university applications?

145
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:16,030
Jing Xichi.

146
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:20,670
I haven't made up my mind.

147
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:22,180
I'm lost.

148
00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,520
Song, what about you?

149
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:27,790
I'm considering

150
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:29,760
whether to apply to Tianhe University.

151
00:05:33,590 --> 00:05:36,500
With these scores,
you're applying to Tianhe University?

152
00:05:36,550 --> 00:05:38,300
Why don't you go to Yenching University?

153
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:39,300
It's near home.

154
00:05:39,620 --> 00:05:40,740
I can take care of my mom.

155
00:05:43,990 --> 00:05:45,940
No. Your mom
has your dad to take care of her.

156
00:05:46,030 --> 00:05:46,790
Besides, Aunt Hao

157
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:47,620
has almost recovered.

158
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:50,280
Haven't you wanted to go
Medical School of Yenching University?

159
00:06:02,670 --> 00:06:04,300
Song,
why do I feel like you've changed?

160
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:06,380
You weren't like this before.

161
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:08,030
What about your ideas?

162
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:10,220
Out of all three years
of senior middle school,

163
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,670
