164
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,640
It's you
who transferred to another class.

165
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,380
It's you
who transferred to another school too.

166
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:17,660
It's also you who keeps saying
you want to study medicine.

167
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,320
Why are you so timid now?

168
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:20,790
Yeah, Song.

169
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:22,420
I think Jing Xichi's right.

170
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,150
You can't give in just because

171
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:25,380
you're afraid to tell your mom

172
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:26,620
you want to study medicine.

173
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:32,990
Enough about me.

174
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:35,380
What about you?

175
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:38,860
Me?

176
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:43,180
A captive bird like me

177
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,260
will probably never

178
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:45,380
be able to escape

179
00:06:45,470 --> 00:06:46,860
the cage of my mom's love.

180
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:47,740
What do you mean?

181
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:49,420
It means

182
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,800
