to apply to Wuan University,

183
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:54,380
saying it's close and convenient for her
to take care of me.

184
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,880
Song,
she's being sarcastic with you.

185
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:00,060
Don't sow discord.

186
00:07:02,350 --> 00:07:02,940
Song.

187
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:04,300
That's not what I meant.

188
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:06,940
I really think

189
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:09,030
you need to think it through again.

190
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,820
I'll talk to my mom.

191
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:19,590
Go.

192
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:27,350
What about you?

193
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:30,260
Are you really
going to give in to your mom?

194
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:33,420
Not really.

195
00:07:34,470 --> 00:07:35,790
I think

196
00:07:35,910 --> 00:07:37,710
that Wuan University
is the most suitable.

197
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:38,860
Besides,

198
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:40,350
I didn't have

199
00:07:40,350 --> 00:07:41,940
any ideas about the future.

200
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:44,060
I was just taking things
one step at a time.

201
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:46,860
But Jing,

202
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:48,670
I didn't expect

203
00:07:48,820 --> 00:07:49,670
your Gaokao score

204
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:50,940
to be so much higher than mine.

205
00:07:52,550 --> 00:07:53,470
Didn't Mr. Xu say

206
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:55,740
that grades can't determine your life?

207
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:00,820
But it can decide that we can have fun

208
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:01,840
this summer holiday.

209
00:08:02,710 --> 00:08:04,500
How about we go out and play
this weekend?

210
00:08:05,470 --> 00:08:05,790
Sure.

211
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:06,760
Where are we going?

212
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:08,040
Who do you want to invite?

213
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,060
Just tell me
who you don't want to invite.

214
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,640
I don't want to invite you.

215
00:08:12,910 --> 00:08:14,380
Master of irony.

216
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:15,230
No.

217
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:16,080
You're stubborn.

218
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:16,790
No.

219
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:17,710
Go on being stubborn.

220
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:18,380
No.

221
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,460
You're still stubborn.

222
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:25,860
You're back.

223
00:08:44,990 --> 00:08:45,620
What's wrong?

224
00:08:53,190 --> 00:08:54,590
Mom, I want to

225
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:57,430
discuss university applications
with you.

226
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:01,070
No need to discuss.

227
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,430
I've discussed it with your dad.

228
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:11,500
We'll enroll you in Medical School

229
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,660
of Yenching University.

230
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:15,710
Medical school?

231
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:17,500
What's wrong?

232
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:19,430
Haven't you always
wanted to study medicine?

233
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:21,710
How did you know?

234
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,350
You're my son.

235
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,620
How could I not know?

236
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,590
You're always secretly

237
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:29,920
reading your dad's medical books.

238
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,860
I already noticed.

239
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:32,990
You father and son

240
00:09:33,070 --> 00:09:34,620
really never give me a moment of peace.

241
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:37,500
One says he wants to quit smoking

242
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,680
but ends up smoking secretly
in the kitchen every day.

243
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,990
He doesn't even clean the ashes

244
00:09:40,990 --> 00:09:41,780
after smoking.

245
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,260
The other one

246
00:09:45,110 --> 00:09:46,430
insists on studying medicine.

247
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:53,430
You two teamed up to lie to me.

248
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:57,830
Sorry, Mom.

249
00:10:00,310 --> 00:10:00,780
Enough.

250
00:10:02,230 --> 00:10:03,500
Why are you apologizing?

251
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:11,430
Let go.

252
00:10:17,260 --> 00:10:18,070
Let go.

253
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:27,830
I know why you

254
00:10:27,830 --> 00:10:29,020
want to stay in Tianhe.

255
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:34,900
I'm recovering well now.

256
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:36,540
I don't need you to take care of me.

257
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:38,900
I don't want to be

258
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,500
a burden to any of you.

259
00:10:42,070 --> 00:10:43,710
If you stay here for me,

260
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,960
