for the rest of my life. You know?

261
00:10:54,710 --> 00:10:55,470
Son.

262
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:02,780
You'll always make me proud.

263
00:11:04,990 --> 00:11:05,590
Your world

264
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:07,160
can't be limited to just this place.

265
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:25,350
Mom.

266
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:26,230
Don't move.

267
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:57,007
(Name: Jing Xichi, University)

268
00:11:57,007 --> 00:11:59,460
(First Choice: Yenching University,
Major: Computer Science)

269
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:09,860
Here, fruit and milk.

270
00:12:10,310 --> 00:12:10,900
Drink some.

271
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:12,310
Rest earlier.

272
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:13,740
Stop looking at the computer.

273
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:14,470
Mom.

274
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:17,740
Tell me which university
I should apply to?

275
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,020
It's up to you.

276
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:20,440
I support you no matter what.

277
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:22,280
Even if you want to repeat your studies,

278
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:23,070
I support you.

279
00:12:23,230 --> 00:12:23,990
Help me

280
00:12:23,990 --> 00:12:24,780
