286
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:37,620
You've grown up.

287
00:12:38,020 --> 00:12:39,710
I believe in your choice.

288
00:12:40,110 --> 00:12:41,230
You'll definitely

289
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:43,190
