Isn't this military training?

326
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:47,620
Qi Qi.

327
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:49,990
What's in your bag?

328
00:15:50,310 --> 00:15:51,430
It looks heavy.

329
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:53,380
I brought some film discs.

330
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:56,260
Who knew we would be hiking?

331
00:15:57,230 --> 00:15:57,780
No.

332
