355
00:17:02,070 --> 00:17:02,740
Jing Xichi.

356
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:03,900
Are you out of your mind?

357
00:17:04,150 --> 00:17:05,340
What a lousy place you picked.

358
00:17:05,870 --> 00:17:07,260
I'll give you one minute

359
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:08,500
