360
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:09,470
You hear me?

361
00:17:10,390 --> 00:17:10,950
Hello?

362
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:12,470
Say something.

363
00:17:14,710 --> 00:17:15,910
