383
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:53,710
We invited him, yet he still grumbled.

384
00:17:54,020 --> 00:17:54,710
Jing Xichi.

385
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:56,020
Do I need to wash these oranges?

386
00:17:56,430 --> 00:17:57,670
Why are you washing oranges?

387
00:17:58,390 --> 00:17:59,470
You bought oranges?

388
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:01,580
Isn't it Chen Huan'er's favorite?

389
00:18:04,820 --> 00:18:05,910
You know

390
00:18:05,950 --> 00:18:07,200
