394
00:18:13,430 --> 00:18:14,710
You get jealous easily.

395
00:18:15,230 --> 00:18:16,230
Alright.

396
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:18,260
Song.

397
00:18:18,710 --> 00:18:20,390
We're the best buddies.

398
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:21,230
Chen Huan'er

399
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:22,060
is at most second.

400
00:18:22,430 --> 00:18:23,500
I know the order

401
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:24,580
