402
00:18:25,540 --> 00:18:26,190
Fine.

403
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,480
I guess you have a conscience.

404
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:29,430
My buddy will always be in my heart.

405
00:18:32,340 --> 00:18:33,630
Can you two say things like that

406
00:18:33,710 --> 00:18:35,020
