413
00:18:53,950 --> 00:18:55,060
Jing Xichi.

414
00:18:57,060 --> 00:18:58,150
Song Cong.

415
00:18:59,300 --> 00:18:59,990
Li Tian.

416
00:19:00,870 --> 00:19:01,990
Is no one here?

417
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:05,300
Did they stand us up?

418
00:19:06,670 --> 00:19:08,150
Jing Xichi must be

419
