00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:09,740
Let's go.

421
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:11,340
Jing Xichi!

422
00:19:14,670 --> 00:19:15,580
Jing Xichi.

423
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:19,710
Happy graduation!

424
00:19:20,390 --> 00:19:21,870
