00:19:55,950 --> 00:19:57,990
Don't just eat oranges
and not help with the chores.

430
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:01,230
Orange peel.

431
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:04,190
Throw here.

432
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:06,020
