443
00:20:21,630 --> 00:20:22,820
You put on makeup?

444
00:20:23,150 --> 00:20:23,740
Let me see.

445
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:25,820
I drew my eyebrows
and wore blush and lipstick.

446
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:29,670
I can't tell at all.

447
00:20:29,710 --> 00:20:30,910
Xinyan, you're still young.

448
00:20:30,910 --> 00:20:32,250
Yet you're already wearing makeup.

449
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:33,500
