00:20:37,390 --> 00:20:38,390
A university student.

453
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:39,390
A university student?

454
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:40,910
Which university are you admitted to?

455
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:42,470
What are we then?

456
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:46,740
We're

457
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:48,300
