00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:16,990
Medical School of Hu University.

469
00:21:17,340 --> 00:21:18,470
Song Cong, what about you?

470
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:21,150
Medical School of Yenching University.

471
00:21:22,260 --> 00:21:23,190
Huan'er, what about you?

472
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:23,710
Me?

473
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:26,230
I applied to Wuan University's Pharmacy.

474
00:21:26,230 --> 00:21:28,700
Qi Qi's going to Jing City
University of Political Science and Law

475
00:21:28,700 --> 00:21:29,820
Jing Xichi, what about you?

476
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:31,870
