477
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:33,430
What major?

478
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,260
Medicine?

479
00:21:35,260 --> 00:21:36,100
No way.

480
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:37,340
I'm studying computer science.

481
00:21:41,630 --> 00:21:42,470
Everyone's going

482
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:43,540
so far away.

483
00:21:53,430 --> 00:21:54,910
I'm here.

484
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:57,300
