491
00:22:19,630 --> 00:22:20,670
Just give me a minute.

492
00:22:33,950 --> 00:22:35,540
In the Mood for Love.

493
00:22:35,910 --> 00:22:36,990
Chungking Express.

494
00:22:37,230 --> 00:22:37,950
Buddha Mountain.

495
00:22:38,390 --> 00:22:39,020
Qi Qi.

496
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:41,150
