506
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:00,870
Why don't we watch something else?

507
00:23:01,390 --> 00:23:03,500
I think you guys are scared.

508
00:23:03,740 --> 00:23:05,260
Who's scared? Let's watch it.

509
00:23:53,060 --> 00:23:53,470
Well...

510
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:54,630
I'll go check on Huan'er.

511
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:29,300
Chef Chen.

512
00:24:29,430 --> 00:24:30,710
Do you need any help?

513
00:24:35,020 --> 00:24:35,820
What are you making?

514
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:36,500
Is it edible?

515
00:24:38,230 --> 00:24:39,060
