524
00:25:05,870 --> 00:25:07,060
Let me check on them.

525
00:25:11,140 --> 00:25:12,190
I'll check on them too.

526
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:15,780
Me too.

527
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:24,340
Pour the juice in here.

528
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:26,780
Wait.

529
00:25:28,500 --> 00:25:30,260
