535
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,470
How dare you laugh at me?

536
00:26:12,190 --> 00:26:14,230
Why don't you wear an apron?

537
00:26:16,060 --> 00:26:17,630
Yes, an apron.

538
00:26:18,580 --> 00:26:20,300
The apron's...

539
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:21,230
Is...

540
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:23,340
Is this an apron?

541
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:24,580
Yes, I'll wear it.

542
00:26:24,780 --> 00:26:25,820
Wear an apron.

543
00:26:27,990 --> 00:26:28,500
Well...

544
00:26:28,950 --> 00:26:30,670
Can you help me tie it?

545
00:26:30,950 --> 00:26:31,390
Sure.

546
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:07,910
All done.

547
00:27:08,630 --> 00:27:09,100
All done?

548
00:27:10,670 --> 00:27:11,390
Huan'er.

549
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,260
What are you doing?

550
00:27:12,430 --> 00:27:13,470
Do you need help?

551
00:27:16,190 --> 00:27:17,150
