553
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,150
Help me get the cookies out.

554
00:27:20,390 --> 00:27:20,990
Wear gloves.

555
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:21,500
Okay.

556
00:27:21,630 --> 00:27:22,340
