557
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,190
I want to play too.

558
00:27:23,260 --> 00:27:23,950
Me too.

559
00:27:23,950 --> 00:27:24,390
Come in.

560
00:27:26,260 --> 00:27:27,630
Crack the eggs first.

561
00:27:27,780 --> 00:27:28,470
