562
00:27:29,430 --> 00:27:29,710
Here.

563
00:27:29,870 --> 00:27:30,300
Okay.

564
00:27:30,860 --> 00:27:31,580
I'll put it here.

565
00:27:31,580 --> 00:27:32,260
Take the eggs.

566
00:27:37,670 --> 00:27:38,740
Add it in here?

567
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:40,500
Yes. Then, throw the trash in...

568
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,020
