572
00:27:46,390 --> 00:27:46,990
I'm fine.

573
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:47,630
Are you okay?

574
00:27:48,150 --> 00:27:48,780
Leave it there.

575
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:49,780
