576
00:27:56,260 --> 00:27:58,100
Here they come, friends.

577
00:27:58,230 --> 00:28:00,150
We're drinking this today.

578
00:28:00,230 --> 00:28:02,060
You only prepared this much liquor?

579
00:28:02,060 --> 00:28:03,470
Are these not enough?

580
00:28:03,470 --> 00:28:05,740
