00:40:51,140 --> 00:40:52,310
Gaokao has ended.

880
00:40:53,950 --> 00:40:55,470
I want to ask you

881
00:40:57,390 --> 00:40:59,060
if you would be my boyfriend.

882
00:41:06,540 --> 00:41:08,390
I should have told you this
a long time ago.

883
00:41:10,310 --> 00:41:11,140
In my eyes,

884
00:41:11,830 --> 00:41:13,620
you have always been
the most special one.

885
00:41:15,020 --> 00:41:16,270
Huan'er, I'm serious.

886
00:41:17,830 --> 00:41:19,060
I don't want to be Doraemon

887
00:41:20,430 --> 00:41:22,580
and be nice to everyone
indiscriminately.

888
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:25,620
I just want to be good to you.

889
00:41:51,350 --> 00:41:53,830
No, Song. I...

890
00:41:54,540 --> 00:41:56,180
I always thought

891
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:58,310
the two of us

892
00:42:00,750 --> 00:42:01,870
were just friends.

893
00:42:06,540 --> 00:42:07,870
I think

894
00:42:09,500 --> 00:42:11,620
we should just stay friends.

895
00:42:20,270 --> 00:42:21,060
I'm sorry.

896
00:42:48,390 --> 00:42:49,020
Xinyan.

897
00:42:50,140 --> 00:42:52,580
Jing Xichi, I hate you.

898
00:42:52,700 --> 00:42:53,660
You...

899
00:42:53,950 --> 00:42:54,950
Don't... You...

900
00:42:55,220 --> 00:42:56,540
I... Where are you going?

901
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:57,310
Liao Xinyan.

902
00:42:58,020 --> 00:42:58,700
Xinyan.

903
00:42:58,950 --> 00:43:00,140
Hurry back.

904
00:43:00,470 --> 00:43:01,620
Where are you going?

905
00:43:35,950 --> 00:43:36,950
Song Cong.

906
00:43:38,950 --> 00:43:39,620
Qi Qi.

907
00:43:41,430 --> 00:43:42,270
Can your matter

908
00:43:42,310 --> 00:43:43,350
wait until tomorrow?

909
00:43:43,790 --> 00:43:45,350
I just want to ask you a question.

910
00:43:49,020 --> 00:43:50,060
If it's Huan'er

911
00:43:50,060 --> 00:43:51,310
that you like,

912
00:43:53,270 --> 00:43:54,910
why did you leave that sentence

913
00:43:54,950 --> 00:43:55,990
in my notebook?

914
00:43:57,580 --> 00:43:58,910
What sentence?

915
00:43:59,750 --> 00:44:01,660
I hope it will last forever

916
00:44:03,620 --> 00:44:04,830
in my time.

917
00:44:07,100 --> 00:44:08,470
You mean The Fountainhead?

918
00:44:09,100 --> 00:44:09,870
I...

919
00:44:15,870 --> 00:44:16,990
I wrote that

920
00:44:16,990 --> 00:44:18,020
for a friend.

921
00:44:23,500 --> 00:44:24,540
I'm sorry.

922
00:45:45,500 --> 00:45:46,500
(That night,)

923
00:45:47,180 --> 00:45:48,750
(I rejected Song Cong.)

924
00:45:49,390 --> 00:45:51,470
(Song Cong rejected Qi Qi.)

925
00:45:52,270 --> 00:45:54,950
(Jing Xichi rejected Liao Xinyan.)

926
00:45:55,830 --> 00:45:57,140
(Only Li Tian)

927
00:45:57,220 --> 00:45:59,870
(had a good chat with Shakespeare.)

928
00:46:00,470 --> 00:46:02,830
Cupid is blindfolded

929
00:46:02,830 --> 00:46:05,350
but breaks into people's hearts.

930
00:46:05,990 --> 00:46:06,870
Cupid.

931
00:46:07,270 --> 00:46:08,140
Li Jianjun.

932
00:46:09,990 --> 00:46:12,060
I'm going to put it out there today.

933
00:46:12,910 --> 00:46:14,580
I won't study medicine.

934
00:46:17,220 --> 00:46:18,060
(Sure enough.)

935
00:46:18,390 --> 00:46:21,100
(It's a truth that a wise man
doesn't fall into the river of love.)

936
00:46:21,540 --> 00:46:23,220
(But even if there's no river of love,)

937
00:46:23,620 --> 00:46:25,180
(there will always be other rivers)

938
00:46:25,270 --> 00:46:27,180
(that we need to cross ourselves.)

939
00:46:44,600 --> 00:46:49,770
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

940
00:46:51,560 --> 00:46:56,640
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

941
00:46:58,410 --> 00:47:03,760
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

942
00:47:04,070 --> 00:47:09,560
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

943
00:47:12,150 --> 00:47:17,170
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

944
00:47:18,960 --> 00:47:24,200
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

945
00:47:25,800 --> 00:47:31,220
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

946
00:47:31,680 --> 00:47:37,180
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

947
00:47:38,380 --> 00:47:42,340
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

948
00:47:42,340 --> 00:47:47,330
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

949
00:47:47,460 --> 00:47:50,890
♪And full of life♪

950
00:47:52,180 --> 00:47:55,640
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

951
00:47:55,640 --> 00:48:00,750
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

952
00:48:01,010 --> 00:48:05,400
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

953
00:48:05,900 --> 00:48:09,800
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

954
00:48:09,800 --> 00:48:14,740
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

955
00:48:14,740 --> 00:48:17,530
♪To know right from wrong♪

956
00:48:19,440 --> 00:48:22,970
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

957
00:48:22,970 --> 00:48:26,220
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

958
00:48:26,380 --> 00:48:32,140
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

959
00:48:32,560 --> 00:48:37,160
♪At just the right time♪

